#feedbackModal_main_8420348\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 21, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104hvq1665702817858.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/hvq1665702817858.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/hvq1665702817858.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"hvq1665702817858\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      More Properties (Field Interface)\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Define field interface definitions for subfields, variable length fields, and database I/O translation.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hvq1665702817858__p_d7502e1_d7503e1_d7504e1\">Normally, you do not need to consider these properties. Define subfields only when accessing existing databases that contain subfields.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hvq1665702817858__section_tmg_d5h_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d990782e58\">Properties</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"hvq1665702817858__ul_llp_d5h_5cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"hvq1665702817858__li_d3671e1_d3672e1_d3673e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rwl1665702711264.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rwl1665702711264.html\" title=\"The length of fixed-length subfields in characters, excluding separators.\">Fixed Length of Subfield</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"hvq1665702817858__li_d3674e1_d3675e1_d3676e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cjw1665702711335.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cjw1665702711335.html\" title=\"Character to be used as the separator between subfields.\">Subfield Separator</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"hvq1665702817858__li_d3677e1_d3678e1_d3679e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vtx1665702711411.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vtx1665702711411.html\" title=\"The method used to identify the beginning of a subfield.\">Identification Type</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"hvq1665702817858__li_d3680e1_d3681e1_d3682e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lsl1665702711481.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lsl1665702711481.html\" title=\"ASCII string that marks a variable-length field.\">Field Identifier</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"hvq1665702817858__li_d3683e1_d3684e1_d3685e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"chv1665702711551.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/chv1665702711551.html\" title=\"ASCII string that marks the first subfield when using variable-length techniques.\">First Subfield Identifier</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"hvq1665702817858__li_d3686e1_d3687e1_d3688e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lvh1665702711625.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lvh1665702711625.html\" title=\"Indicates whether data strings should be translated on database input and output.\">Database I/O Translation</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hvq1665702817858__section_nzc_25h_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d990782e122\">How to</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hvq1665702817858__p_d7784e1_d7785e1_d7786e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lhc1704371292385.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lhc1704371292385.html\" title=\"Create modeled properties using editors available on the More Editors menu. Use a modeled property by clicking the More icon ( icon ) in the appropriate property of an entity or field.\">Working with Modeled Properties</a>\n</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hzd1665702710226.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Modeled Entity Interface</a><p>A Modeled Entity Interface is a Development Object that defines a reusable value for the Database Interface property of a Database Entity.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lnr1704360335272.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Variable-Length Fields</a><p>Variable-length fields store only the actual data in the field, and not the trailing spaces that would be added for a fixed-length field.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_8420348\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_8420348\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "More Properties (Field Interface) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 21, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 More Properties (Field Interface) Define field interface definitions for subfields, variable length fields, and database I/O translation. Normally, you do not need to consider these properties. Define subfields only when accessing existing databases that contain subfields. Properties Fixed Length of Subfield Subfield Separator Identification Type Field Identifier First Subfield Identifier Database I/O Translation How to Working with Modeled Properties Related Links Modeled Entity Interface A Modeled Entity Interface is a Development Object that defines a reusable value for the Database Interface property of a Database Entity. Variable-Length Fields Variable-length fields store only the actual data in the field, and not the trailing spaces that would be added for a fixed-length field. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}